# How many rural businesses are in the 2017 InfoGroup in the three different categories of 'rural'?
# Below, the numbers include Alaska and Hawaii. Those states were not included in the mapping above.
# In the results below, '1' flags rural areas; '0' flags urban areas.

# Note: the Census definition counts nearly twice as many rural businesses as the OMB definition
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
# 1. The OMB definition (metro and micro -politan areas are 'urban'; everything else is 'rural'.
# Metropolitan and micropolitan areas are whole counties.)
print(df['rural_OMB'].value_counts())
